    "As shown in Figure 2, the DMTS simulations (with both generic and system-specific models) with an outer time step of 5 fs and HMR correctly reproduce the STS results within statistical uncertainties.",
    "Overall, with this setup, we obtain a speedup of around 4 compared to STS with 1 fs time step for bulk water simulations corresponding to an increase from 6.59 to 25.03 ns/day (See Table 2).",
